Grimlock continued forward as he grumbled over his "leaders" orders. "Me 
grimlock no dummy, me grimlock King!" He grew closer to the ark.

Scourge and the others followed slowly. "Quetzalcoatl, Mirage you to know how 
to get in the ark, Quetzal, you deal with deffenses, Mirage go stealth and 
open the door for us you are in there after all."

Mirage looked over to the rookie and slowly faded into invisibility, he then 
followed grimlock ahead. 

Scourge then turned to the dinobots, "The rest of you get ready, remember 
this is "the" ark, if one of you get slagged, i'll bring you back to life 
just so i can kill you myself." He reached behind his back and removed a 
large red sword, and a cannon.
